{"tid":1342802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果大家懷疑元朗警黑合作，一定要報ICAC！","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T18:25:39.000Z","uid":48187,"like":170,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"bd6ce4168c900bd26e1d16de210d63a13c2b2bea","tid":1342802,"uid":48187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:58:43.000Z","msg":"只要有片或第一身證據，懷疑黑幫中人(最好有名有姓)向元朗警局決策人(當然最好有警員名）提供利益，作為元朗警局對今晚發生嘅事不採取合理嘅執法行動嘅報酬，就可以舉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有片加人證，證明有警務人員對眼前罪案視而不見都可以報，姐係影到佢唔做野都可以！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢種係corruption allegation，以及普通法嘅公職人員行為失當罪(MIPO)，ICAC一定要開file，起碼多班友查件事！唔好畀警黑合作恆常落去！維護廉潔香港，人人有責！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0490866cf1f57c62c90a0e969f619bb329693c4","tid":1342802,"uid":48187,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:59:28.000Z","msg":"我有嘢講！我要舉報！"},{"pid":"b2fd27997426ab16a23237c9d96d393c44ae170d","tid":1342802,"uid":48187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:59:39.000Z","msg":"我要舉報！"},{"pid":"0d0001b5369ed3a8f5d8dac156167aa07ed77bf3","tid":1342802,"uid":29167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:59:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1338170/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1338170/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返唔到屋企嘅手足入黎!! 有地方落腳!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bbb0947c20d5a76293f2a227dbb8b380cd4547","tid":1342802,"uid":48187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:00:15.000Z","msg":"幫手推推，麻煩大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ador